-- GVK Power Signs a Contract With Hyundai Engineering, Larsen & Toubro Group
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-06-21T06:26:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/gvk-power-signs-a-contract-with-hyundai-engineering-larsen-toubro-group.html

          
          
             GVK Power & Infrastructure Ltd.
signed a contract with Hyundai Engineering Co. and Larsen &
Toubro Ltd. to set up a 800 megawatt gas-based power plant at a
cost of 32 billion rupees in southern Indian state of Andhra
Pradesh, according to an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        